<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（八九寺叫住了我们  说道）</font>

178
00:09:28,800 --> 00:09:29,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也许吧…</font>

179
00:09:29,210 --> 00:09:29,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（我说道  大概  面带笑容）</font>

180
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:36,370
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也许在哪里擦肩而过也说不定  毕竟道路这东西全国都有嘛</font>

181
00:09:36,650 --> 00:09:38,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不  我不是说那个</font>

182
00:09:39,020 --> 00:09:42,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没见过  我只是个匆匆过客而已</font>

183
00:09:45,260 --> 00:09:48,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是  你能够活下来  真是非常感谢</font>

184
00:09:49,020 --> 00:09:50,030
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（然后就那样）</font>

185
00:09:54,660 --> 00:09:54,950
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（没有回头）</font>

186
