00:11:54,940 --> 00:11:55,780
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">咔咔咔</font>

226
00:11:56,400 --> 00:12:02,440
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">要拯救世界  也要拯救女人  这种贪婪才是现代英雄的形象吧</font>

227
00:12:02,640 --> 00:12:04,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没错  是这样</font>

228
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:11,790
