264
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:19,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这样一来就既不能逃也不能躲了</font>

265
00:14:19,920 --> 00:14:22,370
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">本来也既不想逃也不想躲</font>

266
00:14:22,900 --> 00:14:24,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那汝准备怎么做？</font>

